| Math, string, input, alert | reference/functions/general.md |
| barstate, var, varip | concepts/execution_model.md |
| Repainting, HTF | concepts/timeframes.md |
| Known errors | concepts/common_errors.md |
| **Always first** | LESSONS_LEARNED.md |

